title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Fokker VII b retro- starting the engines
description:
In this how to we are going to look at how to start the engines of the Fokker F VIIb tripple engine aircraft. The edition we are going to use is the retro version which is kind of the modernized Fokker VII b aircraft with a lot of components which you will find in modern aircrafts.
